{"tid":2025340,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"擬下月認管有汽油彈和襲擊罪 還柙七個月舞台設計師准保釋陪病母 被告不禁落淚","createTime":"2020-05-20T07:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T08:35:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1aec9c5df634c6eeefe7d5f3c0c94d2c734d81c6","tid":2025340,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:30:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200520/CJR7NYRHWL7AFUXYTTMLQWJHVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200520%2FCJR7NYRHWL7AFUXYTTMLQWJHVE%2F&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=def5a9ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200520%2FCJR7NYRHWL7AFUXYTTMLQWJHVE%2F&h=bf3ee79e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200520/CJR7NYRHWL7AFUXYTTMLQWJHVE/</a><br />\n<br />\n年輕舞台設計師涉於示威期間企圖向警員投擲汽油彈，另於「連儂牆」襲擊摘去其頭套的男子，他早前在區域法院表態將會認罪，還柙待下月中求情和判刑。惟被告希望短期保釋回家，今向高等法院申請保釋。法官李運騰批准他以嚴苛的條件擔保外出，包括20萬元現金及不得離開居所，但容許他到醫院陪伴病母。聽到申請獲批，被告不禁落淚。"},{"pid":"74c19a3c628f0ef0ced0d086083ba97632e3fcd6","tid":2025340,"uid":328890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:31:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6996894b836089595cb7efbcdddfa2fba3d3522","tid":2025340,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"74c19a3c628f0ef0ced0d086083ba97632e3fcd6","tid":2025340,"uid":328890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:31:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cbb7aefbe4ad6db2433e99c39abfdddf097a1f3","tid":2025340,"uid":319932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r